                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There is a significant bonus to getting SCM3 over SCM2.  If your mana is a real concern, I wouldn't hesitate to finish this off.  With that being said, I would recommend ER2.  ER is in my opinion one of the best investments for aa's.  Having a 1000 (1500 with ER3) hp insta-cast, manaless rune is very nice.  The reuse time on it is 10 minutes, so you can use it almost every time charm breaks when you are soloing.
<br />

<br />
TD2 and TD3 will also be great investments for you to help out with the charm soloing.  MC and GM are great to have along with MGB, especially in raid situations.  But I think if you are spending most of your time soloing then I would still choose either ER or TD as the first to max out.  However if your time is mainly spent in LDoN or BoT, then I would probably go with SCM and MC to help keep mana up.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=398646" target="_blank" class="postlink">Fadnae Vantempla</a>
