                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I would go with SCM3 first.  I have read somewhere in the hundreds of posts I have seen on how it works that it basically ups your spec rating by something like 100% at level 3, so you get the biggest benefit in the one you have over 50 in.
<br />

<br />
I got up to ER2, but haven't gotten ER3 yet (180 aa pts now) and haven't found a time where the difference between 1000 hp and 1500 hp would have made a difference.  Others may have, but 1000hp for me was always enough to get the heal to land or get the mob under control, or cast arcane rune.
<br />

<br />
Getting mana preservation items to me made a huge difference in my mana pool and my playing style.  I would strongly recommend you finish SCM3 before going on to anything else, especially for LDoN where you don't get much med time.
<br />

<br />
Aallynth</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
