                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">In terms of effectiveness, the third rank of SCM is worth the first two... combined.
<br />

<br />
Rank 1 adds 5%.
<br />
Rank 2 adds 10% (total of 15%).
<br />
Rank 3 adds 15% (total of 30%).
<br />

<br />
Succeeding in a Specialization check will lower the mana cost (scaled by your effective specialization skill) and lower the chance to fizzle.
<br />

<br />
Our primary specialization skill caps at 200, with scm3 that will cap at 252 (hardcoded skill cap for all skills, at least thats what I was told at the fan faire)
<br />

<br />
Our non-primary specialization skills cap at 50, with scm3 that is an effective 65.
<br />

<br />
--
<br />
One note:  Most of our spells are alteration, but a few ones that dont:
<br />
Abjuration:<a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3199&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Arcane Rune</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3343&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Rune of Zebuxoruk</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3242&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Guard of Druzzil</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3342&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Howl of Tashan</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1697&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Recant Magic</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3302&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Shield of Maelin</a>
<br />
Divination:<a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3359&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Word of Morell</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=4408&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Color Cloud</a>
<br />
Conjuration:<a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3358&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Bliss</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=2569&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Glamorous Visage</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=2568&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Horrifying Visage</a>, 
<br />
Evocation:<a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3348&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Torment of Scio</a>, <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3349&source=Live" target="_blank" class="postlink">Insanity</a></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=378985" target="_blank" class="postlink">Tashim</a>, 65th Enchanter
